description: Help develop a model that let people effortlessly query databases using simple, natural language commands, without the need for complex SQL syntax. Whether you're a business analyst, data scientist, or a developer, the Text2SQL model bridges the gap between you and your data, making data retrieval intuitive and efficient. Training data for this task is based on some open-sourced Text2SQL dataset, it may contain some inaccurate queries. The task creator has done extensive cleaning and manual review for the final validation set.
The Text2SQL Agent Model is a model that converts natural language questions into SQL queries.
